    General Stores in Bandra West, Mumbai

    General Stores in Bandra West, Mumbai

    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Bandra West, Mumbai from the list given above.
